    {
      "id": "t-9PHSPYLqDoVGs0GDxpQV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 222.87540954996643,
      "y": 450.0124035499864,
      "width": 1752,
      "height": 94.50000000000001,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "【目的】把 NanoClaw 在本地跑起来，配 DeepSeek-V4 凭证，处理 Docker 首次安装 + verify failed 两次人工对话，最后在项目里装上 Superpowers v5。\n\n【里程碑】Step 5 跑通 `pnpm run chat ping → pong` = 完整链路通电（CLI → service → Docker → Claude Agent SDK → DeepSeek-V4）。\n\n【关键判断】走 DeepSeek 官方 Anthropic 兼容层（api.deepseek.com/anthropic）—— NanoClaw 一行代码不用改。",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "【目的】把 NanoClaw 在本地跑起来，配 DeepSeek-V4 凭证，处理 Docker 首次安装 + verify failed 两次人工对话，最后在项目里装上 Superpowers v5。\n\n【里程碑】Step 5 跑通 `pnpm run chat ping → pong` = 完整链路通电（CLI → service → Docker → Claude Agent SDK → DeepSeek-V4）。\n\n【关键判断】走 DeepSeek 官方 Anthropic 兼容层（api.deepseek.com/anthropic）—— NanoClaw 一行代码不用改。",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": false,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
