    {
      "id": "t-cxoC4i1hanAKlRBvWl7Q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 524,
      "y": 646.6,
      "width": 1452,
      "height": 226.8,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "在终端执行：\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork && cd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork\n\n# git clone NanoClaw v2 到 nanoclaw-v2 子目录（NanoClaw 推荐目录名）\ngit clone https://github.com/qwibitai/nanoclaw.git nanoclaw-v2\ncd nanoclaw-v2\n\n# 查看版本\ncat package.json | grep version\n```",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在终端执行：\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork && cd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork\n\n# git clone NanoClaw v2 到 nanoclaw-v2 子目录（NanoClaw 推荐目录名）\ngit clone https://github.com/qwibitai/nanoclaw.git nanoclaw-v2\ncd nanoclaw-v2\n\n# 查看版本\ncat package.json | grep version\n```",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": false,
