    {
      "id": "t-S4xL34f7SsZSvWm1BIDH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 527.2914216210322,
      "y": 953.7000004140625,
      "width": 1452,
      "height": 453.6,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "> 跑下一步 `bash nanoclaw.sh` 时，setup:auto 第一个 prompt 是 `Standard setup vs Advanced`。Standard 默认连 `api.anthropic.com`，先在这里把后端模型决策清楚。\n\n最终决策：\n\n```\n✅ 后端：DeepSeek-V4（通过 DeepSeek 自家 Anthropic 兼容层）\n✅ Endpoint：https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic\n✅ Auth Token：sk-c884c8f74942422dac699bcdb3c2c1b8\n✅ 模型名：deepseek-v4-pro\n✅ NanoClaw 模式：Standard setup（默认 Enter）\n   通过预设环境变量 NANOCLAW_ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL + NANOCLAW_ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN\n   让 setup:auto 跳过 advanced 交互，直接生效\n```\n\n把以下字段写入项目根 `.credentials.yaml`（已 .gitignore，凭证不进 Git）：\n\n```yaml\napi_keys:\n  deepseek_v4:\n    key: \"sk-c884c8f74942422dac699bcdb3c2c1b8\"\n    anthropic_base_url: \"https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic\"\n    openai_base_url: \"https://api.deepseek.com\"\n    default_model: \"deepseek-v4-pro\"\n```",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "> 跑下一步 `bash nanoclaw.sh` 时，setup:auto 第一个 prompt 是 `Standard setup vs Advanced`。Standard 默认连 `api.anthropic.com`，先在这里把后端模型决策清楚。\n\n最终决策：\n\n```\n✅ 后端：DeepSeek-V4（通过 DeepSeek 自家 Anthropic 兼容层）\n✅ Endpoint：https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic\n✅ Auth Token：sk-c884c8f74942422dac699bcdb3c2c1b8\n✅ 模型名：deepseek-v4-pro\n✅ NanoClaw 模式：Standard setup（默认 Enter）\n   通过预设环境变量 NANOCLAW_ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL + NANOCLAW_ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN\n   让 setup:auto 跳过 advanced 交互，直接生效\n```\n\n把以下字段写入项目根 `.credentials.yaml`（已 .gitignore，凭证不进 Git）：\n\n```yaml\napi_keys:\n  deepseek_v4:\n    key: \"sk-c884c8f74942422dac699bcdb3c2c1b8\"\n    anthropic_base_url: \"https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic\"\n    openai_base_url: \"https://api.deepseek.com\"\n    default_model: \"deepseek-v4-pro\"\n```",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": false,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a0015",
      "seed": 1988840353,
