      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "在终端执行：\n\n```bash\n# 预设环境变量（让 setup:auto 自动用 DeepSeek 兼容 endpoint，跳过 advanced 交互）\nexport NANOCLAW_ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=\"https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic\"\nexport NANOCLAW_ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=\"sk-c884c8f74942422dac699bcdb3c2c1b8\"\n\n# 跑官方一键部署脚本\nbash nanoclaw.sh\n```\n\n进入 setup:auto 交互界面后：\n\n- \"How would you like to begin?\" → 选 **Standard setup** 直接 Enter\n- 后续 channel 选 **cli**，display name 自取",
      "textAlign": "left",
