    {
      "id": "t-YysDJFIPWmIPXSs5aOxA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 524,
      "y": 1841.4758545985096,
      "width": 1452,
      "height": 699.3000000000001,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "没装 Docker 时，nanoclaw.sh 会通过 `brew install --cask docker-desktop` 自动装，期间会触发三件事，逐一应对：\n\n**A. sudo 密码 prompt**\n\n终端会出现 `Password:`（不是图形弹窗）。在那里输 macOS 用户登录密码，按 Enter（输入时不显示字符是正常的）。\n\n**B. Docker Desktop 首次启动 Welcome 弹窗**\n\n```\nWelcome to Docker\n[Work] [Personal]\nUsing Docker for work?\n[Work email address] [Continue]\nOr\n[Google] [GitHub] [Create an account]\n[Skip ←右上角]\n```\n\n点右上角 **Skip**——本地跑容器不需要 Docker 账号登录。\n\n**C. nanoclaw.sh 的 \"looks stuck\" 误警**\n\n```\n▲  This looks stuck — no output from the container step for the last 60 seconds.\n◆  What now?\n│  ● Keep waiting\n│  ○ Ask Claude to take a look\n```\n\n选 **Keep waiting**（默认 Enter）——本来就在装 Docker，不是 bug。\n\n确认 Docker daemon 已就绪：\n\n```bash\ndocker --version    # Docker version 29.4.2\ndocker info | head  # Server 段必须存在 → daemon 在跑\n```",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "没装 Docker 时，nanoclaw.sh 会通过 `brew install --cask docker-desktop` 自动装，期间会触发三件事，逐一应对：\n\n**A. sudo 密码 prompt**\n\n终端会出现 `Password:`（不是图形弹窗）。在那里输 macOS 用户登录密码，按 Enter（输入时不显示字符是正常的）。\n\n**B. Docker Desktop 首次启动 Welcome 弹窗**\n\n```\nWelcome to Docker\n[Work] [Personal]\nUsing Docker for work?\n[Work email address] [Continue]\nOr\n[Google] [GitHub] [Create an account]\n[Skip ←右上角]\n```\n\n点右上角 **Skip**——本地跑容器不需要 Docker 账号登录。\n\n**C. nanoclaw.sh 的 \"looks stuck\" 误警**\n\n```\n▲  This looks stuck — no output from the container step for the last 60 seconds.\n◆  What now?\n│  ● Keep waiting\n│  ○ Ask Claude to take a look\n```\n\n选 **Keep waiting**（默认 Enter）——本来就在装 Docker，不是 bug。\n\n确认 Docker daemon 已就绪：\n\n```bash\ndocker --version    # Docker version 29.4.2\ndocker info | head  # Server 段必须存在 → daemon 在跑\n```",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": false,
      "angle": 0,
