      "text": "Step 5\n\n处理 setup 末尾 verify\nfailed + Claude 诊断（人工\n对话）",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Step 5\n\n处理 setup 末尾 verify failed + Claude 诊断（人工对话）",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": false,
