    {
      "id": "t-3OGpXq1W3iEaDTocQ6Dv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 524,
      "y": 2618.737927299255,
      "width": 1452,
      "height": 1228.5000000000002,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "nanoclaw.sh 走到末尾会跑 `setup/verify.ts` 自检。前面选了 **Skip for now（不接 IM channel）**，所以 verify 报：\n\n```\nCONFIGURED_CHANNELS: github\nREGISTERED_GROUPS: 0\nSTATUS: failed\n```\n\n这不是 bug，是\"没绑 IM = 没注册 messaging group\"的预期失败。\n\n**A. 让 Claude 接管诊断**\n\n```\n◇  Want me to ask Claude to diagnose this?\n│  ● Yes / ○ No\n```\n\n选 **Yes**。\n\n**B. Claude 给的诊断结论 + 它给的命令是错的**\n\nClaude 看完日志后会说要跑：\n\n```bash\npnpm exec tsx scripts/init-first-agent.ts\n```\n\nsetup:auto 询问 `Run this command? Yes/No` → 选 Yes → 执行 → 报错：\n\n```\nMissing required args: --channel, --user-id, --platform-id, --display-name\n```\n\n`init-first-agent.ts` 是为绑定真实 IM channel 设计的，纯本地路径不适用。Claude 诊断**结论对，命令错**——这是预期内的真实场景。\n\n**C. 改用正确的 `init-cli-agent.ts`（纯本地路径）**\n\nsetup:auto 退出后，service 仍在跑。在终端执行：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2\npnpm exec tsx scripts/init-cli-agent.ts \\\n  --display-name \"muyu\" \\\n  --agent-name \"Andy\"\n```\n\n预期输出：\n\n```\nCreated agent group: ag-XXXXXXXXXX (cli-with-muyu)\nWired cli: mg-XXXXXXXXXX -> ag-XXXXXXXXXX\nInit complete.\n  owner:   cli:local\n  agent:   Andy [ag-XXXXXXXXXX] @ groups/cli-with-muyu\n  channel: cli/local\nRun `pnpm run chat hi` to talk to your agent.\n```\n\n**D. 用 `pnpm run chat` 做闭环 ping/pong**\n\n```bash\npnpm run chat \"ping, please reply with pong only\"\n```\n\n终端打印 `pong` —— 完整链路通了。",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "nanoclaw.sh 走到末尾会跑 `setup/verify.ts` 自检。前面选了 **Skip for now（不接 IM channel）**，所以 verify 报：\n\n```\nCONFIGURED_CHANNELS: github\nREGISTERED_GROUPS: 0\nSTATUS: failed\n```\n\n这不是 bug，是\"没绑 IM = 没注册 messaging group\"的预期失败。\n\n**A. 让 Claude 接管诊断**\n\n```\n◇  Want me to ask Claude to diagnose this?\n│  ● Yes / ○ No\n```\n\n选 **Yes**。\n\n**B. Claude 给的诊断结论 + 它给的命令是错的**\n\nClaude 看完日志后会说要跑：\n\n```bash\npnpm exec tsx scripts/init-first-agent.ts\n```\n\nsetup:auto 询问 `Run this command? Yes/No` → 选 Yes → 执行 → 报错：\n\n```\nMissing required args: --channel, --user-id, --platform-id, --display-name\n```\n\n`init-first-agent.ts` 是为绑定真实 IM channel 设计的，纯本地路径不适用。Claude 诊断**结论对，命令错**——这是预期内的真实场景。\n\n**C. 改用正确的 `init-cli-agent.ts`（纯本地路径）**\n\nsetup:auto 退出后，service 仍在跑。在终端执行：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2\npnpm exec tsx scripts/init-cli-agent.ts \\\n  --display-name \"muyu\" \\\n  --agent-name \"Andy\"\n```\n\n预期输出：\n\n```\nCreated agent group: ag-XXXXXXXXXX (cli-with-muyu)\nWired cli: mg-XXXXXXXXXX -> ag-XXXXXXXXXX\nInit complete.\n  owner:   cli:local\n  agent:   Andy [ag-XXXXXXXXXX] @ groups/cli-with-muyu\n  channel: cli/local\nRun `pnpm run chat hi` to talk to your agent.\n```\n\n**D. 用 `pnpm run chat` 做闭环 ping/pong**\n\n```bash\npnpm run chat \"ping, please reply with pong only\"\n```\n\n终端打印 `pong` —— 完整链路通了。",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": false,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
