      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "切换到 Claude Code，确认在 `nanoclaw-v2` 目录：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2\n```\n\n在 Claude Code 中执行：\n\n```\n/plugin marketplace add obra/superpowers-marketplace\n/plugin install superpowers@superpowers-marketplace\n```\n\n重启 Claude Code 让 SessionStart h 生效：\n\n```bash\nexit\nclaude\n```",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "切换到 Claude Code，确认在 `nanoclaw-v2` 目录：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2\n```\n\n在 Claude Code 中执行：\n\n```\n/plugin marketplace add obra/superpowers-marketplace\n/plugin install superpowers@superpowers-marketplace\n```\n\n重启 Claude Code 让 SessionStart h 生效：\n\n```bash\nexit\nclaude\n```",
