      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "在终端执行：\n\n```bash\n# 看 agent group 的物理产物（一个 group = 一份 CLAUDE.md + 一个独立 Docker 容器）\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2\nls groups/cli-with-muyu/\ncat groups/cli-with-muyu/CLAUDE.md | head -30\ncat groups/cli-with-muyu/container.json\n```\n\n会看到 `groups/cli-with-muyu/` 下有 `CLAUDE.md`（agent 的 system prompt）+ `container.json`（容器配置）+ `.claude-fragments/`（Skill 注入点）+ `settings.json`。",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在终端执行：\n\n```bash\n# 看 agent group 的物理产物（一个 group = 一份 CLAUDE.md + 一个独立 Docker 容器）\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2\nls groups/cli-with-muyu/\ncat groups/cli-with-muyu/CLAUDE.md | head -30\ncat groups/cli-with-muyu/container.json\n```\n\n会看到 `groups/cli-with-muyu/` 下有 `CLAUDE.md`（agent 的 system prompt）+ `container.json`（容器配置）+ `.claude-fragments/`（Skill 注入点）+ `settings.json`。",
